                    <div class="card-body">
                        <p class="text-muted">
                            The application follows a three-tier architecture:
                        </p>
                        <ul>
                            <li><strong>Frontend Tier:</strong> EJS templates with Bootstrap 5 for responsive UI, JavaScript for client-side interactions</li>
                            <li><strong>Backend Tier:</strong> Node.js Express server handling API requests, file uploads, database operations, and third-party API integrations</li>
                            <li><strong>AI/ML Tier:</strong> Python Flask API running TensorFlow models for disease detection and prediction</li>
                            <li><strong>Database Tier:</strong> MySQL database storing user predictions and historical analysis data</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>
